snippet.title: Little Friends: Puppy Island - Official Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Little Friends: Puppy Island will be available on Steam and Nintendo Switch on June 27, 2023. Watch the latest trailer for a tour of Puppy Island, and learn about various activities like doing photo shoots with puppies, playing with them, dressing them up with accessories, hunting for treasure, and more.

#GameTrailers #Gaming
